      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you\u2019re getting a car that\u2019s ready to hit the road immediately! It runs beautifully and the interior is still looking great. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable set of wheels that won't break the bank, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
