    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, equipped with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal mechanical grip. The chassis remains sharp thanks to the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a well-sorted suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS system inspection and fluid service, ensuring the rod bearings and valvetrain operate within peak tolerances. A mechanically robust performance machine that balances track-ready precision with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
