      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly well-loved? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly such a gem! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been my favorite companion for weekend getaways. I've taken really good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
