    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, delivering linear torque up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from M-specific subframes and a variable M differential lock that ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing service and updated throttle actuators, mitigating common S65 failure points. The hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback missing in modern EPS systems. This example presents in strong mechanical health with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
